dataIdInfo.idAbs: This point data layer represents addresses for Calumet County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Calumet_Addresses_2017.gdb.[Site address points represent the location of site or service delivery addresses assigned by local governments.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [Site Address Points]

dataIdInfo.suppInfo:
Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation, please visit http://www.calumetmaps.com/data.html
This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.
